node.text:
Hot days and sultry nights call for a little extra support to keep up with hydration. Cue Sakara Beauty Water Drops, a concentrated blend of 72 naturally-occurring ionic trace minerals (including magnesium)—and now in exclusive cocktails at @thesurflodge until August 30. 

Hydrate on a cellular level with our Sultry Watermelon Sandia and Sonic Sunshine Lemonade, or add Beauty Water Drops to any cocktail on The Surf Lodge menu, and get ready to glow.

node.text:
Save This: Beauty + The Boost Parfait

When you incorporate both our Metabolism Super Powder and our Metabolism Super Bar (aka The Metabolism Duo) into your routine, you’ll experience real, plant-powered results with every blissful bite. This parfait contains both—combining the functional plant ingredients of the super duo to make this the metabolism-revving breakfast of your dreams:

✔️Horsetail Extract: a natural diuretic that eases bloat 
✔️Gymnema Sylvestre: an Ayurvedic herb that supports healthy blood sugar and cortisol levels
✔️L-Glutamine: an amino acid that supports energy and digestion, and curbs cravings 
✔️Kelp Extract: an antioxidant from brown seaweed that helps shed excess weight
✔️​​Brown Rice and Pea Protein: 12 grams of clean plant protein that fuel muscles to counteract age-related muscle loss

What recipes are you dreaming up with the best-selling Metabolism Duo? Get creative in the kitchen with the link in bio.

NEW MEAL ALERT: High Vibe Honeydew Salad 

We’re head over heals for honeydew. This refreshingly sweet, glow-boosting melon packs 90% water along with an impressive collection of electrolytes—like potassium, magnesium, sodium, and calcium—within an intricate web of fiber. This helps your body absorb H2O slowly, offering a steady stream of hydration and nutritions. 

Prepare to feel electric at the link in bio.

Save This: Aphrodite's Ice Cubes

Add a beautiful dose of functional hydration to your drink with these glow-inducing cubes. Simply pour water into your ice cube mold, add 1-3 dropperfuls of Beauty Water Drops per cube, and freeze. Drop into alkaline water, seltzer, or lemonade and sip. As the ice cubes melt, feel the 72 naturally-occurring ionic trace minerals (including magnesium) working to plump your cells, elevate your energy, and boost your glow. 

Optional: Exercise your artistry and add edible flowers to the mold prior to freezing. 

Head to the link in bio to purchase this client-favorite wellness essential.

node.text:
Fire up a healthy metabolism anytime, anywhere with the Metabolism Duo—back in stock now. Enjoy our Metabolism Super Powder and Metabolism Super Bar together to experience the full-spectrum benefits of a healthy, thriving metabolism, or choose one depending on what your day has in store.

Choose Metabolism Super Powder if you're looking to rev your mornings and ease bloat first thing. Add to coffee, blend into smoothies, or shake vigorously with 8-12 oz water, nut milk, or coconut water. 

Choose Metabolism Super Bar if you're on-the-go and looking to take the power of plants with you. The caffeine-free, functional blend will fuel your workouts and keep up with your packed agenda. 

Questions? Feel free to ask below 👇 in the comments.
